data.description: 3 bedroom 2 full bath with over 1800 sq ft single level two car home! Walkin shower and Roman tub. Huge open floor plan with island kitchen. Plantation shutters on most windows and both sliders (bedroom & family) that look over the beautiful tropical landscape backdrop. Mountains are right across the cul de sac (front & back) and create a beautiful private view. Home is placed facing north on a corner for the perfect amount of early sun. Shaded by the neighbor to the west, home never gets the intense direct heat. Pool, spa & clubhouse and green belts that keeps the community with a more resort feel. Welcome to Laughlin, feel free to stay on vacation.
